  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Also at 6th level, you have improved upon your Scientific Ninja Beast's programing giving it a definitive roll in combat.</p><p> Choose one of the following: </p><p>• Striker: Your S.N.B gains the Multiattack trait, allowing it to make two attacks using its natural weapons.</p><p> • Caster: Your S.N.B gains the ability to learn jutsu and a number of Jutsu Slots equal to 1/4th your Science-Nin level (rounded down).<br /> You can spend 3 Weeks of downtime programing a jutsu into your S.N.B and it can learn a number of jutsu equal to half your proficiency bonus.<br /> The highest ranked jutsu your S.N.B can learn is always one rank lower than your current highest rank jutsu known as indicated by your class table.</p><p> • Defensive: Your S.N.B gains a bonus to its AC equal to 1/3rd your Proficiency bonus (rounded down) </p><p>• Lurker: Your S.N.B gains the Lethal Attack trait.</p><p> Once per turn, your S.N.B can deal extra damage to one creature it hits with an attack if another enemy of the target is within 5 feet of it.</p><p> This extra damage is Xd8.  (X = Half your Science-Nin Level)</p>",
